<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/particles.js/2.0.0/particles.min.js"></script>
    <title>Security Alert - Suspicious Activity Detected</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: #0a192f;
            color: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        #particles-js {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: rgba(13, 25, 48, 0.9);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 1rem;
        }

        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #ff4757;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff4757;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #a4b0be;
        }

        .details {
            background: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.1);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .timer {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff4757;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        button {
            background: transparent;
            color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #ff4757;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #ff4757;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="particles-js"></div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="alert-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
        <h1>Security Alert</h1>
        <p>Our systems have detected suspicious automated activity from your account. Multiple unauthorized attempts to access data have been blocked.</p>
        
        <div class="details">
            <p>üö´ <strong>Violation Type:</strong> Automated Data Harvesting</p>
            <p>‚ö° <strong>Request Rate:</strong> Exceeded normal threshold</p>
            <p>üîí <strong>Status:</strong> Account temporarily restricted</p>
        </div>

        <p>For security reasons, your access has been temporarily suspended.</p>
        <div class="timer">
            Cooldown: <span id="countdown">300</span>s
        </div>
        
        <button onclick="location.reload()">Verify Identity</button>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Initialize particles.js
        particlesJS('particles-js', {
            particles: {
                number: { value: 80 },
                color: { value: '#ff4757' },
                shape: { type: 'circle' },
                opacity: {
                    value: 0.5,
                    random: true
                },
                size: {
                    value: 3,
                    random: true
                },
                move: {
                    enable: true,
                    speed: 2
                }
            }
        });

        // Countdown timer
        let timeLeft = 300;
        const countdownEl = document.getElementById('countdown');
        
        const timer = setInterval(() => {
            timeLeft--;
            countdownEl.textContent = timeLeft;
            
            if (timeLeft <= 0) {
                clearInterval(timer);
                countdownEl.parentElement.textContent = 'Verification Available';
            }
        }, 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>